@page "/chat"
@rendermode InteractiveServer
<PageTitle>Chat</PageTitle>


<card class="h-50">
    <cardHeader>Chat History</cardHeader>
    <cardBody TextAlignment="TextAlignment.Justified">
        <div class="col-12 d-flex flex-column h-25">
            <div class="flex-grow-1 overflow-auto"
                 style="height: 25vh; overflow-y: auto">
                @((MarkupString)@responseToDisplay.ToString())
            </div>
            @*  <textarea class="form-control" rows="15" readonly value="@((MarkupString)@responseToDisplay)"></textarea>  *@
            
        </div>
    </cardBody>
</card>
<br />
<textarea class="form-control" rows="9" @bind=@UserInput />
<br />
<button type="button" class="btn btn-success" @onclick="OnSubmitClick">Submit</button>
<br />
<p><strong>News:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>To get the latest headline news, ask: &quot;Please provide me with the headline news.&quot;</li>
    <li>For specific topics, replace &quot;headline&quot; with &quot;Business,&quot; &quot;Technology,&quot; &quot;Sports,&quot; &quot;Science,&quot; or &quot;Health.&quot; For example: &quot;Please give me the latest technology news.&quot;</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Weather:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>To check the weather in a particular city, ask: &quot;How&#39;s the weather in [City], [State], [Country]?&quot; If you&#39;re in the United States, you can omit the country. For instance: &quot;How&#39;s New York, NY weather?&quot;</li>
</ul>
